              ~ TELAME WEBROOT STRUCTURE GUIDE ~
                          14/11/2010 -
-----------------------------------------------------------------

                 webroot
                  / | \         [c] = Controller Name (Hyphenated)
                 /  |  \        [a] = Action Name (Hyphenated)
                /   |   \       [v] = View Name (Hyphenated)
               /    |    \      (#) = Resources for a view(s)
              /     |     \
             /      |      \
          css      js       img
           |        |        |
     >>>  new      new       |\  <<< TEMPORARY (see FIXME in hrl)
         / |       / \       | \
        /  |      /   \      |  \
       /   |   common [c]    |   \
      /    |     |    / |    |    \
     /     |    (#)  /  |    |     \
  common  [c]       /   |  common  [c]
    |    / |       /    |    |    / |
   (#)  /  |   common  [v]  (#)  /  |
       /   |     |      |       /   |
      /    |    (#)    (#)     /    |
  common  [v]              common  [v]
    |      |                 |      |
   (#)    (#)               (#)    (#)